{"tid":1642621,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[法律團隊入] 可唔可以跟蹤下呢單嘢?","createTime":"2019-10-09T19:46:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T23:39:27.000Z","uid":266174,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e885cd84e4432692757a9030c1a572c47e9cd965","tid":1642621,"uid":266174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T19:46:05.000Z","msg":"一手資料<br />\n<br />\n喺外國做緊法律相關嘅嘢: 中國有人舉報政府官員貪污， 因為中國同外國未必有引渡條例， 所以請香港出全球通緝令， 逼香港做白手套。 其中一個罪名係舉報人係香港組織暴動， 就算嗰個人冇去過香港都冇所謂。<br />\n<br />\n1. 有冇傳媒朋友願意跟蹤一下而家香港發出全球通緝令有幾多張? <br />\n2. 中國到底用咩辦法逼香港政府代佢出通緝令？<br />\n3. 香港政府手上有冇告緊非香港人喺香港組織暴動？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請隨便提議呢單嘢可以點用。"},{"pid":"9c5f246aae7ae8a13aecfe40d41f6043e05c2168","tid":1642621,"uid":224303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T19:49:19.000Z","msg":"幫推 緊要到樓主要特登開account嚟開post"},{"pid":"4a63b2c6e9f69626307348400b33cb2b6a05bd26","tid":1642621,"uid":154702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T19:54:03.000Z","msg":"有趣<br />\n透露多少少<br />\n完整啲"},{"pid":"e80b3cc72e4a8a94781b472a66852716f27cfb3e","tid":1642621,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T23:38:41.000Z","msg":"靠香港法律界真係食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到依家都完全冇任何法律意見討論"},{"pid":"88fead229c9e4a180b7bfa1d6ecae8bc3d9a9d23","tid":1642621,"uid":313764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T23:39:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hLCPmok.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhLCPmok.jpg&h=d80cc8eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成日話要爭取國際線支持，我依家開左個英文版連儂牆啦，全部同我入去瘋狂貼文宣!<br />\n<br />\n[English] LIHKG Lennon Wall ver 1.0<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1640768\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1640768</a>"}]}